<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang=en>
  <head>
    <meta charset=utf-8>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/tacit-css.min.css"/>
    <title>The Vulnerable Movie Center</title>
    <style>
      body {
        padding-top:0px;
      }
      .thin {
        margin-top:5px;
        margin-bottom:5px;
      }
      #search-form {
        text-align:right;
        margin-bottom:0;
        padding-bottom:0;
      }
      #search-result {
        display: none;
      }
      #movie-data {
        padding-bottom:10px;
      }
      #playbill {
        vertical-align:top;
        margin:10px;
      }
      #movie-details {
        display:inline-block;
        width:40%;
      }
      #search-term {
        font-style: italic;
      }
    </style>
    <script src="js/search.js"></script>
    <script src="js/auth_local.js"></script>
    <script src="js/auth_session.js"></script>
    <script src="js/submit_review.js"></script>

  </head>
  <body>
    <section>
      <h1 style="margin-top:5px">The Vulnerable Movie Center</h1>
      <hr class="thin">
      <hr class="thin">
    </section>

    <section id="movie-data">
      <img id="playbill" src="images/good-bad-ugly.jpg"/>
      <div id="movie-details">
        <b>Title:</b> The Good, the Bad and the Ugly<br/>
        <b>Year:</b> 1966<br/>
        <b>Directed by:</b> Sergio Leone<br/>
        <b>Starring:</b> Clint Eastwood, Lee Van Cleef, Eli Wallach<br/>
        <b>Duration:</b> 177 min.<br/>
        <br/>
        <b>Plot:</b>
        <p>During the Civil War, two men forming an uneasy alliance as bounty hunting scammers have to fight against a third in a race to find a treasure in gold buried in a remote cemetery.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
      <div style="text-align: center">
        <button type="button" style="background: #275a90;color: #fff;" onclick="return auth_local()">Token Local Storage</button>
        <button type="button" style="background: #275a90;color: #fff;" onclick="return auth_session()">Token Session Storage</button>
        <button type="button" style="background: #275a90;color: #fff;" onclick="location.href='session/jwt/cookie';">Token Cookie</button>
      </div>
    <section id="comments", style="margin-top:10px">
      <form method="post" action="reviews">
        <fieldset>
          <textarea id='123'name="newReview" cols="80" rows="5" placeholder="Add your review"></textarea>
            <div>You need a token to submit a review.</div>
        </fieldset>
        <fieldset>
          <button type="button" style="background: #275a90;color: #fff;" onclick="submit_review()">Submit</button>
        </fieldset>
      </form>
      <hr>
      <h2>Comments</h2>
      <dl>
        <% reviews.forEach(review => {%>
          <dt><%= review.username %></dt><dd><%-review.review %></dd>
        <% }); %>
      </dl>
    </section>
  </body>
</html>
